sections.markdown:
Have you ever wondered who earns more: a pilot or a doctor?

This interactive allows you to explore the data within the [2014 Annual Survey of Hours and Earnings][1] release. It illustrates the occupations with the highest and lowest earnings, allows you to compare occupations with similar salaries and even tests your knowledge via a couple of quizzes.

####Median gross full-time annual earnings by occupation, Great Britain, April 2014

<ons-interactive url="https://www.ons.gov.uk/visualisations/nesscontent/dvc205/ashe.html#panel=y2&occ=0" full-width="true" title="Median gross full-time annual earnings by occupation, Great Britain, April 2014"/>
